name: Nino Vida
description: People who know me well can describe me as a very positive, active, sociable and optimistic person. No matter what happens in my life I always try to smile and not to give up. In my company it is not possible to feel boring, I enjoy this life, even small details which can seem not so noticeable. I am romantic, affectionate and imaginative in the relationships. Devotion and faithfulness are basic elements for my future relationship. I am interested in philosophies of self-improvement and personal growth. I care both about my physical and inner beauty. I am very good in massage. It is a big pleasure for me to spend time outdoors, to relax far from the busy city life on the lap of nature, I like making photos and catching some interesting moments. Traveling and learning new cultures are also my big passions!!!
